txt.en: 'That is right, you ugly beast. Get in there!'
'That is right, stay, or you will taste my axe!'
'Prepare to face the wrath of ice, fire, and acid, Outsiders.'
'Your last battles were nothing compared to what you have just unleashed.'
'He comes...and you had best ready yourselves. It is unlikely that you will survive.'
'I did not think you would come so far....In fact -- oh!'
'Strangers against the Men of Dunland...This should prove interesting.'
'Saruman of Many Colours, you are most welcome here.'
'You cannot win, Duv√≥diad! This is our turf.'
'Fight well, my minions. I know you will not bring shame upon Isengard this day.'
'Very exciting battle! I am beginning to like you strangers.'
'These little warriors will rue the day they challenged us.'
'Well done indeed. I do not think Saruman will be pleased that his warriors fell to contestants such as you....'
'I am...quite surprised by this turn of events. But the fight was exciting -- I will give you that.'
'Hmm. I am increasingly surprised by how well you have done....'
